@startuml visitor_flow
actor Visitante
participant "Next.js Frontend" as Frontend
participant "API Route" as API
participant "Use Case" as UseCase
participant "Prisma Repo" as Repo
database "Supabase" as DB

Visitante -> Frontend: Acessa Home Page
Frontend -> API: GET /api/eventos
API -> UseCase: execute()
UseCase -> Repo: findUpcoming()
Repo -> DB: SELECT * FROM eventos...
DB --> Repo: Result Set
Repo --> UseCase: Entity[]
UseCase --> API: Entity[]
API --> Frontend: JSON Response
Frontend --> Visitante: Exibe lista de eventos

@enduml
